            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Hastings Borough Council are seeking to appoint a suitably qualified and experienced contractor to provide a Leisure Management Service at their Summerfields Leisure and Falaise Fitness Centres.</P>
               <P>The Council encourage bidders to visit the centres in order to fully prepare their proposals. To facilitate this, a site visit day has been arranged on Thursday 5 October 2017. Bidders should contact procurement@hastings.gov.uk to register their interest and obtain details about the agenda for the day.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
