               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>Hastings Borough Council are seeking to appoint a suitably qualified and experienced contractor to provide a Leisure Management Service at their Summerfields Leisure and Falaise Fitness Centres.</P>
                  <P>The Council will award to the contractor a service concession to manage the centres, with a right to exploit the services to be delivered at the centres and retain any payment which is received from third party users. The Council will grant to the contractor leases to both centres to enable them to deliver the services under this arrangement.</P>
                  <P>The contract is for an initial period of 5 years with two optional 24-month extensions (at the sole discretion of the Council) — maximum 9 years in total.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
